    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AUS nEw sEdLano",
      "AIR NEW ZEALAND s DC-8 s link New Zealand and\nthe South Pacific with Australia, the Orient and\nNorth America. Their powerful fanjet engines and\nluxury interiors ensure superb comfort. The symbol\non the tail fin is the Koru which had its place on the\nsternposts of questing Maori canoes that probed\nPacific distances in another time.\nPOSTCARD\nAIR NEW ZEALAND LIMITED\nAIR NEW ZEALAND House, Queen St., Auckland, N.Z.\nPlace\nStamp\nHere\n1565A PRINTED IN NEW ZEALAND\n2015.166,0037"
    ],
